title: Shopping Bag, "H.C. Andersen laeser...", mid-1980s
description: Recto: "H.C. Anderson laeser eventyr for damilien Collin". Verso: Odensk, multicolor photomechanical reproduction of Niels Larsen Steven painting: "Hank op I din fortid/-ga pa Museum".  Photomechanical reproduction of articles and photos pertaining to Anderson & Anderson House.
